					<p>Something is wrong with your reply links. It&#8217;s using the wrong kind of quotes. Instead of single quotes in the A link, it&#8217;s using double quotes, which it should not be doing.</p>
<p>What does the actual PHP code in your comments.php look like? Post a copy on <a href="http://wordpress.pastebin.com" rel="nofollow">http://wordpress.pastebin.com</a> and give me a link to it, so I can examine it.</p>
