				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>I don&#8217;t understand your response.</p>
<p>If you&#8217;ve made the changes to your theme as I describe in the article, and the Reply link doesn&#8217;t show, then you still need to enable the Threaded Comments option on the Settings-&gt;Discussion screen.</p>
<p>The reply link <em>will not show</em> unless threaded comments are turned on.</p>
<p>That&#8217;s all there is to it. I cannot explain it any better than that.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

