					<p>Thanks, that last suggestion sounds sensible &#8211; and in effect gives a non-paging-dependent permalink for each comment. Where would such code go though? I&#8217;ve not had much experience hacking  WP at this kind of level, so I may need to see if there is anyone out there that could be motivated to help out.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

